---
title: Melty Mozzarella Chicken Pomodoro Bake with Crispy Panko
description: As the temperature continues to plummet, it’s impossible not to daydream about a soul-warming dish. Well, folks, the search is over. This bubbly bake has Tuscan-spiced chicken and tender bites of al dente penne cloaked in a savory tomato sauce. It’s topped off with toasted breadcrumbs and melty mozzarella before being broiled to golden-brown perfection. This one-pan wonder is guaranteed to satisfy all cold weather cravings. We’re all about making dreams come true.
